item.content:encoded: [vc_row overlay_dotted=""][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1502799901090{padding-right: 72px !important;}"][vc_accordion one_active="true"][vc_accordion_tab title="For how much time do I need to invest on SEO?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1504506199896{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]Google keeps on updating its algorithm every now & then for better user experience; hence one needs to keep his SEO strategy implementation at its best.Â SEO is an ongoing process as your competitors always try hard to fetch your place on the ranking table, hence executing SEO for a particular time period is never a promising idea. On the other way round, one cannot expect that he/she will invest once & rule the 1st place in search engines for life-time. Nothing is permanent,[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What are Long tail keywords?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1504507486765{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]As search engines have advanced, weÂ now include more detail and complexity within ourÂ searches as weÂ seek to find what weâreÂ looking for faster than ever before Â Long tail keywordsÂ are longerÂ keyword phrases, which are highlyÂ specific to a userâs search query.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What is SMO?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1504506692404{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]SEO is the technique of optimizing your website and getting it placed in the high ranking of search results. It is one of the most preferred mode of Internet Marketing.Â There are hundreds of search engines across the web, Iâm sure you will use most of them every single day. Google, which is said to have an 85% market share.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Why is SEO important?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1504507131602{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]Well, if consider thatÂ 93% of all online experiences begin with a search engine, like Google, then you can safely say that your customers are using search engines too.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Do you know online marketing?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1504506850050{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]Online marketing, which is also calledÂ internet marketingÂ orÂ onlineÂ advertising, is any tool, strategy or method of getting the company name out to the public. The advertisements can take many different forms and some strategies focus on subtle messages rather than clear-cut advertisements[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What will be the process after I sign up?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1504506962458{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]The SEO Project manager will have a quick word with you to make sure that things are on the same page. NextÂ His team will subsequently start with the review & competitorâs analysis andÂ Once completed, the SEO PM will then send you the most likely keywords to be optimized.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Why you should focus on long tail keywords?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1504506463897{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]When it comes to organic keyword rankings, is not to rank for a few top keywords that remain the same over time, but to focus on a much larger number of natural language searches by targeting keyword topics that grow and change rapidly over time.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Where Is your work in-line with the latest updates of Google algorithms? "][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1504507205224{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]Absolutely, our team spends a lot of time in researching about latest developments in the SEO world Â hence our work is always abreast with latest updates of Google algorithms.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What mean of cost of outsourcing to SEO agencies?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1504507389597{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}"]SEO agencies will probably run on a day rate and break down what you need from them and package it into a price based on the cost of their time.Â SEO agencies tend to run higher than freelancers but you are paying for their experience, ethics, resourcesÂ and effectiveness..[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]
